reviewText: The movie is so bad that is good. Fun to watch when you want to rest your brain.
So bad it was hard to watch.  Have not finished it yet.
Great old school movie with the Bruce Lee imitators & the villain in WAY OF THE DRAGON!!!!!!!
Only Dragon Lee does a good job and maybe Bruce Le.
Fight sequences were well done but video quality was sub par and audio not never good
I agree with the previous reviewer. It is cheesy, campy fun. Bruce Li is fun to watch. And the music is laughable.

Excellent and campy seventies Bruce Lee exploitation movie!!! All the Bruce Lee imitators are in it although Bruce Li will always be the best!! Picture wasn't too good but that's perfect because it adds to the fun grindhouse effect which works with it plus it was free so what can you expect?
